<p style="color: #222222; font-size: 12.8px;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="color: #222222; font-size: 12.8px;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">We realize that a malpractice claim can be a distressing and difficult event for any physician or healthcare professional. It is our goal to provide you with the most supportive and aggressive claims defense services in the industry to alleviate as much uncertainty and ensure the most successful resolutions possible.</span><u></u><u></u></p>
<p style="color: #222222; font-size: 12.8px;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Regardless of the outcome of your recent claim, the quality of your experience with your claim specialist and your defense attorney is extremely important to us. To help us understand your satisfaction with the service you received, we invite you to complete a survey by clicking on the link below.</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a style="font-size: medium;" href="${event.parm2}">Click here to take the survey</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="color: #222222; font-size: 12.8px;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">By sharing your experiences, you will help us advance our goal of providing exceptional service.<br /><br />Thanking you in advance for your time and cooperation.<br /><br />Sincerely,</span><u></u><u></u></p>
<p style="color: #222222; font-size: 12.8px;"><strong><span style="color: darkorange;">Timothy Smith</span></strong>&nbsp;| <span style="color: darkgray;">NORCAL Group</span><br /><span style="color: darkgray;">Senior Vice President, Claims</span></p>]]></message_html>
